fields.name: LabSubnetName
fields.description: The name given to the subnet within the lab.

fields.name: ResourceId
fields.description: The resource ID of the subnet.

fields.name: SharedPublicIPAddressConfiguration
fields.description: Properties that virtual machines on this subnet will share.

fields.name: UseInVMCreationPermission
fields.description: Indicates whether this subnet can be used during virtual machine creation (i.e. Allow, Deny).

fields.name: UsePublicIPAddressPermission
fields.description: Indicates whether public IP addresses can be assigned to virtual machines on this subnet (i.e. Allow, Deny).

fields.name: VirtualNetworkPoolName
fields.description: The virtual network pool associated with this subnet.
